## Summary

**The golden rule**: When in doubt, check `llms.txt` first. It contains the comprehensive guide to this codebase. These rules enforce the patterns documented there and ensure consistency across all development.

Remember: This project prioritizes **reusability**, **consistency**, and **maintainability**. Every piece of code should be written with these principles in mind.
